<ac:AIStudioUserControl x:Class="AIStudio.Wpf.Controls.Demo.Views.IntroduceView"
             xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
             xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml"
             xmlns:mc="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/markup-compatibility/2006" 
             xmlns:d="http://schemas.microsoft.com/expression/blend/2008" 
             xmlns:local="clr-namespace:AIStudio.Wpf.Controls.Demo.Views"
             xmlns:ac="https://gitee.com/akwkevin/aistudio.-wpf.-controls"
             mc:Ignorable="d" 
             x:Name="userControl"
             d:DesignHeight="450" d:DesignWidth="800"
             Style="{DynamicResource AIStudio.Styles.AIStudioUserControl}">
    <UserControl.Resources>
        <ac:ObjectListConverter x:Key="ObjectListConverter"/>
    </UserControl.Resources>
    <Grid>
        <FlowDocumentScrollViewer>
            <FlowDocument FontSize="{Binding Path=FontSize, RelativeSource={RelativeSource AncestorType=FlowDocumentScrollViewer}}" 
                          FontFamily="{Binding Path=FontFamily, RelativeSource={RelativeSource AncestorType=FlowDocumentScrollViewer}}" 
                          LineHeight="15">
                <Paragraph >本控件库收集了一些常用的控件，可选主题为MahApps和MaterialDesign</Paragraph>
                <Paragraph >下面介绍一款应用该控件库的权限管理框架
                    <Hyperlink ac:HyperlinkAttach.ViewInBrower="True" NavigateUri="https://gitee.com/akwkevin/aistudio.-wpf.-aclient" >https://gitee.com/akwkevin/aistudio.-wpf.-aclient</Hyperlink>
                </Paragraph>
                <Paragraph >该框架为.NET Core5.0+Wpf（CS-重点）/Ant Design Vue版（此处不在介绍）/Vant(手机端-稍微介绍下)</Paragraph>
                <Paragraph>该框架旨在极大的提高开发效率</Paragraph>
                <Paragraph>
                    使用技术栈：
                    <LineBreak />
                    <LineBreak />
                    后端：由Colder.Admin.AntdVue改造完成的，请参照（本处不在介绍，请看原作者的介绍，本文重点为Wpf）
                    <Hyperlink ac:HyperlinkAttach.ViewInBrower="True" NavigateUri="https://github.com/Coldairarrow/Colder.Admin.AntdVue" >https://github.com/Coldairarrow/Colder.Admin.AntdVue</Hyperlink>
                    <LineBreak />
                    另外扩展了Quartz，WebSocket实现即时聊天及实时消息推送，WorkflowCore实现了OA流程。
                    <LineBreak />
                    <LineBreak />
                    前端：Wpf
                    <LineBreak />
                    安装包下载地址：
                    <LineBreak />
                    <Hyperlink ac:HyperlinkAttach.ViewInBrower="True" NavigateUri="http://121.36.12.76:5000/setup/">http://121.36.12.76:5000/setup</Hyperlink>
                    <LineBreak />
                    自动升级地址:
                    <LineBreak />
                    <Hyperlink ac:HyperlinkAttach.ViewInBrower="True" NavigateUri="http://121.36.12.76:5000/update/">http://121.36.12.76:5000/update</Hyperlink>
                    <LineBreak />
                    具体技术实施：
                    <LineBreak />
                    项目采用Prism的MVVM，并采用严格分层模式，极大的增加聚合度，降低耦合度，完全兼容BS端，使用相同的API接口。
                    <LineBreak />
                    1.AIStudio.Wpf.Service与后台交互的逻辑。
                    <LineBreak />
                    2.本项目使用MahApps.Metro.NET45的扁平风格，并集成了Xceed.Wpf.ToolKit，HandyControl，MaterialDesignInXamlToolkit等其它优秀框架的控件，并且修改成MahApps.Metro.NET45的统一主题。
                    <LineBreak />
                    3.控件的使用可以在AIStudio.Wpf.DemoPage中查看，并且支持运行时代码复制。
                    <LineBreak />
                    4.代码生成器，可以生成直接可运行的界面，加快开发速度。
                    <LineBreak />
                    <LineBreak />
                    相关链接:
                    <LineBreak />
                    该框架链接,欢迎点星支持:
                    <Hyperlink ac:HyperlinkAttach.ViewInBrower="True" NavigateUri="https://gitee.com/akwkevin/aistudio.-wpf.-aclient">https://gitee.com/akwkevin/aistudio.-wpf.-aclient</Hyperlink>
                    该框架Vue链接,欢迎点星支持:
                    <Hyperlink ac:HyperlinkAttach.ViewInBrower="True" NavigateUri="https://gitee.com/akwkevin/aistudio.-vue.-aclient">https://gitee.com/akwkevin/aistudio.-vue.-aclient</Hyperlink>
                    <LineBreak />
                    个人GitHub,欢迎点星支持:
                    <Hyperlink ac:HyperlinkAttach.ViewInBrower="True" NavigateUri="https://gitee.com/akwkevin">https://gitee.com/akwkevin</Hyperlink>
                    <LineBreak />
                    个人博客:
                    <Hyperlink ac:HyperlinkAttach.ViewInBrower="True" NavigateUri="https://www.cnblogs.com/akwkevin/">https://www.cnblogs.com/akwkevin/</Hyperlink>
                    <LineBreak />
                    .NET Core3.0 下载:
                    <Hyperlink ac:HyperlinkAttach.ViewInBrower="True" NavigateUri="https://dotnet.microsoft.com/download">https://dotnet.microsoft.com/download</Hyperlink>
                    <LineBreak />
                    MahApps.Metro:
                    <Hyperlink ac:HyperlinkAttach.ViewInBrower="True" NavigateUri="https://mahapps.com/">https://mahapps.com/</Hyperlink>
                    <LineBreak />
                    HandyControl:
                    <Hyperlink ac:HyperlinkAttach.ViewInBrower="True" NavigateUri="https://handyorg.github.io/handycontrol/" >https://handyorg.github.io/handycontrol/</Hyperlink>
                    <LineBreak />
                    Xceed.Wpf:
                    <Hyperlink ac:HyperlinkAttach.ViewInBrower="True" NavigateUri="https://github.com/xceedsoftware/wpftoolkit/" >https://github.com/xceedsoftware/wpftoolkit/</Hyperlink>
                    <LineBreak />
                    <LineBreak />
                    个人QQ:80267720(欢迎技术交流及技术合作)
                    <LineBreak />
                    QQ技术交流群:51286643
                </Paragraph>
            </FlowDocument>
        </FlowDocumentScrollViewer>
        <StackPanel HorizontalAlignment="Right" VerticalAlignment="Top">
            <Button Content="开始向导" Command="{Binding ShowCommand}"  Style="{DynamicResource AIStudio.Styles.Button}">
                <Button.CommandParameter>
                    <MultiBinding Converter="{StaticResource ObjectListConverter}">
                        <Binding ElementName="userControl" Path="ControlStatus"/>
                        <Binding ElementName="userControl" Path="CodeToggleButton"/>
                        <Binding ElementName="userControl" Path="OptionsPanel"/>
                        <Binding ElementName="testBtn" Path="."/>
                    </MultiBinding>
                </Button.CommandParameter>
            </Button>
            <Button x:Name="testBtn" Content="向导最后一个节点" Margin="0,5,0,0" Style="{DynamicResource AIStudio.Styles.Button}"/>
        </StackPanel>
    </Grid>
</ac:AIStudioUserControl>
